  <brief_title>Gut Hormone Profiling in Obese Patients With Type 2 Diabetes (MK-0000-134)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Gut Hormone Profiling in Peripheral Blood After Bariatric Surgery in Obese Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will examine changes in various gut-derived hormones in obese type 2 diabetic
      patients before and after elective bariatric surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
